data.description: Assumable loan for qualified VA buyers! Welcome to this beautifully updated home, where the spacious layout and vaulted ceilings create an airy and inviting atmosphere. The modern kitchen blends style with functionality, and seamlessly connects to the living area. Large sliding doors allow for an abundance of natural light and provide easy access to the expansive deck, ideal for relaxation or entertaining guests. The primary bedroom features an ensuite bathroom and a generous walk-in closet. Situated on a large lot, this property boasts a private yard, providing a serene outdoor space for gardening or leisure activities. Additionally, the convenience of an attached garage enhances this home's appeal, ensuring comfort and practicality for its residents. Conveniently located near public transportation, shopping and recreation. This home is a true gem, offering a blend of contemporary design and comfortable living.
